WEBVTT

00:00:12.896 --> 00:00:13.813
DAD: COMING HOME?

00:00:13.896 --> 00:00:15.146
I'm almost there.

00:00:26.396 --> 00:00:27.730
YU-CHING: I'M ALMOST THERE

00:00:27.813 --> 00:00:29.271
Let's grab a snack.

00:00:53.271 --> 00:00:56.355
OKAY! I'LL WAIT FOR YOU
READ: 10:37 p.m.

00:01:07.146 --> 00:01:07.980
Yu-ching.

00:01:09.688 --> 00:01:10.688
Yu-ching.

00:01:15.188 --> 00:01:16.938
Wang Yu-ching!

00:01:22.646 --> 00:01:24.813
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:25.938 --> 00:01:28.146
THE GHOST FORGE

00:01:28.646 --> 00:01:30.980
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT
CENTRAL DISTRICT PRECINCT

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:39.355
You again?

00:01:40.688 --> 00:01:43.188
We've been waiting so long

00:01:43.271 --> 00:01:45.605
and you still fob us off
with small-time cops.

00:01:46.646 --> 00:01:47.813
Where's the captain?

00:01:49.813 --> 00:01:50.938
The precinct chief?

00:01:53.063 --> 00:01:55.730
I'm in charge of this case. Let's talk.

00:01:56.313 --> 00:02:00.396
When did you last have a run-in
with the leader of the Heilung Clan?

00:02:01.146 --> 00:02:05.063
My client runs a legitimate business.
He has no links to the triads.

00:02:08.646 --> 00:02:10.480
We have records showing

00:02:10.563 --> 00:02:12.605
that since 2018,

00:02:12.688 --> 00:02:16.396
there have been three turf disputes
and dozens of brawls.

00:02:18.188 --> 00:02:20.980
My client is just a passive shareholder.

00:02:21.063 --> 00:02:23.730
He's not privy to these minor disputes.

00:02:24.188 --> 00:02:25.605
Minor disputes?

00:02:25.688 --> 00:02:28.230
The Heilung Clan just won
a bid worth 100 million,

00:02:28.313 --> 00:02:30.355
but got wiped out before seeing a dime.

00:02:30.938 --> 00:02:33.396
Mr. Liu, you're a ruthless devil.

00:02:38.230 --> 00:02:41.855
You can't catch the culprit
so you harass innocent citizens instead.

00:02:42.688 --> 00:02:44.855
It's taxpayer's money
that pays your wages.

00:02:44.938 --> 00:02:47.855
Do you know
how much I pay in taxes each year?

00:02:48.730 --> 00:02:50.021
-Mr. Shen.
-Yes.

00:02:50.105 --> 00:02:51.355
Take a note of this.

00:02:52.105 --> 00:02:54.105
The next time I pay taxes,

00:02:54.188 --> 00:02:57.105
buy some dog food while you're at it
to feed to these dogs!

00:03:06.271 --> 00:03:08.396
Sorry, excuse me.

00:03:08.480 --> 00:03:09.605
Hurry, let's go.

00:03:10.646 --> 00:03:12.813
SHE DIDN'T COME HOME
SO I WENT LOOKING FOR HER

00:03:12.896 --> 00:03:14.271
AND FOUND HER BACKPACK

00:03:17.063 --> 00:03:20.188
Please. You must find my daughter.

00:03:20.771 --> 00:03:23.188
It's just the two of us now. She…

00:03:23.688 --> 00:03:25.563
She's all I have.

00:03:25.646 --> 00:03:26.688
I'm begging you.

00:03:30.813 --> 00:03:34.563
FOUND HER BACKPACK IN LANE 48

00:04:10.230 --> 00:04:12.396
No… no!

00:05:04.396 --> 00:05:08.646
According to the Shen-Lung Crown Prince,
Chen Chi-sha is likely behind all this.

00:05:08.730 --> 00:05:11.188
He promised him
all sorts of rewards and powers.

00:05:11.271 --> 00:05:13.521
But first he had to
find primal souls for him.

00:05:18.146 --> 00:05:19.521
What's a primal soul?

00:05:25.146 --> 00:05:29.438
Heard of three souls and seven spirits?
The primal soul is one of the three souls.

00:05:29.521 --> 00:05:32.938
Hellspawn are refined
from the primal souls of innocent victims.

00:05:33.771 --> 00:05:35.396
The way those triads died.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:37.855
I bet Chen Chi-sha used hellspawn.

00:05:37.938 --> 00:05:40.105
And it has to be linked to the Demon King.

00:05:42.146 --> 00:05:43.188
Take a look at this.

00:05:43.938 --> 00:05:48.021
A girl called Wang Yu-ching went missing.
I found signs of the Demon King nearby.

00:06:03.063 --> 00:06:04.855
WUMENG OCCULTIST KIDNAPS GIRL

00:06:06.105 --> 00:06:07.188
What's this?

00:06:13.521 --> 00:06:15.771
The Demon King
wants to enter the Human Realm

00:06:15.855 --> 00:06:19.980
before your tasks are complete
and your successor takes over.

00:06:25.313 --> 00:06:29.063
-Did you handle it?
-That's between me and him.

00:06:29.146 --> 00:06:32.021
A girl's life is at stake.
I'll look into it for you.

00:06:34.063 --> 00:06:35.105
Thanks.

00:06:43.938 --> 00:06:45.980
Actually, there's one more thing.

00:06:48.896 --> 00:06:53.980
Chao got a search warrant for Liu's place.
Maybe you can take a look.

00:06:54.063 --> 00:06:56.271
Check for any evidence
of sorcery or ghosts.

00:07:02.355 --> 00:07:04.938
I know he probably burnt down your home.

00:07:05.688 --> 00:07:09.396
But we've been working really hard lately
to get all the evidence we can,

00:07:09.480 --> 00:07:11.896
so that scumbag,
Liu Kuan-fu, will finally--

00:07:11.980 --> 00:07:13.605
You're worried I'll kill him?

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:19.355
You'll be there. What can I do?

00:07:19.938 --> 00:07:23.771
And I'm trying to atone for my sins.
I can't go adding to them.

00:07:42.813 --> 00:07:45.021
-Hurry, Chao's already on his way.
-Okay.

00:07:45.521 --> 00:07:46.355
Han Chieh.

00:07:47.605 --> 00:07:49.313
Can I ask you something?

00:07:57.813 --> 00:07:59.896
Is Hsiang still around here somewhere?

00:08:03.646 --> 00:08:06.438
He didn't go when the time came,
so remained earthbound.

00:08:07.313 --> 00:08:08.855
He can't be far away.

00:08:10.146 --> 00:08:13.063
But I've never seen him,
even with my third eye opened.

00:08:13.146 --> 00:08:14.855
-I really don't under--
-Sister Lo.

00:08:15.438 --> 00:08:16.980
You were both very close.

00:08:18.271 --> 00:08:19.813
But for both your sakes,

00:08:20.855 --> 00:08:22.771
you should move on with your life.

00:08:23.813 --> 00:08:25.230
He might be staying away,

00:08:25.313 --> 00:08:27.896
so that you can forget
about the fire and move on.

00:08:29.563 --> 00:08:32.146
How about you?
You've been down to see your parents.

00:08:32.730 --> 00:08:33.980
How are they doing?

00:08:38.688 --> 00:08:39.730
I can't face them.

00:08:49.646 --> 00:08:50.938
That's why

00:08:51.855 --> 00:08:54.188
whenever I encounter tricky family issues,

00:08:54.271 --> 00:08:57.563
I always tell people to cherish
their family while they can.

00:08:58.063 --> 00:09:02.021
Because they won't be around forever.
But people always take offence.

00:09:07.021 --> 00:09:09.855
-If you're all right, I'd better be off.
-Okay.

00:09:16.188 --> 00:09:18.355
DONGFENG SNACKS

00:09:24.688 --> 00:09:25.730
-Sis.
-Yes?

00:09:25.813 --> 00:09:28.980
-Stop cleaning. Come and eat.
-Okay.

00:09:32.188 --> 00:09:34.271
A different dish every day.

00:09:34.355 --> 00:09:36.980
-You're a genius.
-That goes without saying.

00:09:37.063 --> 00:09:39.896
What choice did I have
with a glutton like you for a sis?

00:09:41.230 --> 00:09:42.855
Don't pinch me.

00:09:43.438 --> 00:09:45.563
Eat up. See if it's any good.

00:09:52.230 --> 00:09:55.105
Any idea how lucky you are
having a genius kid brother

00:09:55.188 --> 00:09:57.105
cook for you every day?

00:10:28.646 --> 00:10:29.855
Holy shit.

00:10:30.646 --> 00:10:33.480
Why is Liu's place
full of wronged spirits?

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:40.980
-Captain, this is all we've found so far.
-Okay.

00:10:42.646 --> 00:10:45.480
Hey, I've looked everywhere
and can't find a thing.

00:10:45.563 --> 00:10:48.563
-Chao, this place is full of ghosts.
-Oh?

00:10:52.521 --> 00:10:54.605
…CLAIMS TWO LIVES
…DISPUTE TURNS FATAL

00:11:25.521 --> 00:11:26.521
What do you want?

00:11:27.021 --> 00:11:28.146
I want him dead.

00:11:28.938 --> 00:11:30.730
He got me killed.

00:11:33.188 --> 00:11:34.396
COMMAND

00:11:35.396 --> 00:11:36.438
Black Command Token?

00:11:37.730 --> 00:11:40.563
The Underworld permitted me
to take his life.

00:11:40.646 --> 00:11:43.646
Wherever he goes, I go.

00:11:44.563 --> 00:11:45.646
Same for them.

00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:02.230
Hey, what kind of a hellhole is this?

00:12:03.896 --> 00:12:06.063
They're all people
that Liu Kuan-fu killed.

00:12:07.146 --> 00:12:10.521
-They want revenge.
-Can't we perform a cross-over ritual?

00:12:12.396 --> 00:12:13.938
They have a Black Command Token.

00:12:14.021 --> 00:12:17.646
Retribution is banned in the Human Realm,
but not down in hell.

00:12:17.730 --> 00:12:20.271
The Underworld has jurisdiction
over revenge there.

00:12:20.355 --> 00:12:21.646
Even gods can't interfere.

00:12:23.813 --> 00:12:25.521
All right, let's call it a day.

00:12:27.396 --> 00:12:28.271
Let's go.

00:12:42.771 --> 00:12:46.355
DONGFENG MARKET

00:12:52.771 --> 00:12:54.063
Who is she?

00:12:54.730 --> 00:12:55.563
What do you want?

00:12:58.355 --> 00:13:00.855
Something weird happened
while I was handling a case

00:13:00.938 --> 00:13:02.896
in the Third Crown Prince's temple.

00:13:03.688 --> 00:13:07.063
-We couldn't find this dead guy's soul.
-I've handled that already.

00:13:07.146 --> 00:13:10.105
The culprit's been caught
and the primal souls returned.

00:13:10.188 --> 00:13:11.396
I helped out too.

00:13:12.313 --> 00:13:15.855
Yes, I heard.
That's why I thought it was weird.

00:13:15.938 --> 00:13:18.813
Hey, I asked around at other temples.

00:13:19.355 --> 00:13:21.105
There are other victims.

00:13:22.896 --> 00:13:23.771
How many?

00:13:23.855 --> 00:13:26.063
At least six.

00:13:30.980 --> 00:13:32.938
Is it who I think it is?

00:13:33.896 --> 00:13:35.146
Chen Chi-sha?

00:13:38.730 --> 00:13:41.480
I thought he'd retired already?
Why would he do this?

00:13:41.563 --> 00:13:43.730
-It must be the Demon King's doing.
-What?

00:13:45.230 --> 00:13:47.938
That's messed up. We're in big trouble.

00:13:49.063 --> 00:13:51.813
Why don't the gods
get rid of these demons themselves?

00:13:51.896 --> 00:13:53.730
Why do they let them run loose?

00:13:54.521 --> 00:13:58.396
Miss, the gods cannot
meddle directly in human affairs.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:14:00.771
Especially those
humans must face themselves.

00:14:02.271 --> 00:14:06.730
However, when demons
try to commit evil through others,

00:14:06.813 --> 00:14:11.146
the gods can issue orders
allowing agents from above to handle it.

00:14:12.188 --> 00:14:13.855
So I'm the unlucky sucker.

00:14:15.605 --> 00:14:17.438
What if you lose to the demon?

00:14:23.563 --> 00:14:25.480
Then I lose. What else can I do?

00:14:27.313 --> 00:14:30.146
Hey, show a little backbone, will you?

00:14:30.230 --> 00:14:33.521
Hey, Chen Chi-sha killed so many people.

00:14:34.271 --> 00:14:35.230
Don't you care?

00:14:36.730 --> 00:14:37.980
I'm retiring soon.

00:14:38.063 --> 00:14:41.146
A superior god or agent from above
should take care of this.

00:14:41.730 --> 00:14:42.896
What use am I?

00:14:42.980 --> 00:14:44.813
Listen to you.

00:14:45.730 --> 00:14:48.230
You're right. You're useless.

00:15:14.605 --> 00:15:17.230
The Demon King's back
and people keep dying.

00:15:17.313 --> 00:15:20.271
-And you do nothing?
-You think it's a game?

00:15:20.355 --> 00:15:21.563
It's not that simple.

00:15:22.688 --> 00:15:24.938
As gods,
we have all these rules to follow.

00:15:25.021 --> 00:15:28.563
Those nagging fuddy-duddies up there
are so strict.

00:15:28.646 --> 00:15:31.480
If I make a move
without their permission,

00:15:31.563 --> 00:15:33.938
then I'll be breaking the rules.

00:15:35.313 --> 00:15:39.271
Do you want me to get trapped
under a mountain like that monkey?

00:15:40.021 --> 00:15:43.063
Why do gods and demons
treat everyone like pawns in a game?

00:15:43.146 --> 00:15:45.646
Always making lackeys or agents
do your dirty work.

00:15:46.271 --> 00:15:49.105
War between gods and demons
is the last thing anyone wants.

00:15:49.688 --> 00:15:53.813
If we were to fight in our true forms,
then the world would come to an end.

00:15:55.146 --> 00:15:57.688
You just don't want
to get your hands dirty.

00:15:57.771 --> 00:15:59.146
You don't care if we die.

00:16:02.271 --> 00:16:05.646
Are you really that scared
of fighting the Demon King again?

00:16:09.271 --> 00:16:10.938
I know I don't have much choice.

00:16:12.105 --> 00:16:13.563
But I don't think I'd win.

00:16:15.396 --> 00:16:19.063
Fair enough.
The Demon King came prepared this time.

00:16:20.730 --> 00:16:22.188
I don't think you will either.

00:16:23.271 --> 00:16:27.271
Hey, aren't you supposed to root for me
and tell me I've got this?

00:16:29.188 --> 00:16:30.896
But then I'd be lying to you.

00:16:31.605 --> 00:16:36.521
Gods don't interfere with human free will,
much less tell you what to do.

00:16:39.146 --> 00:16:41.105
You're afraid of taking responsibility.

00:16:43.146 --> 00:16:45.521
If things go badly,

00:16:45.605 --> 00:16:50.355
you can just hold your hands up and say
the Third Crown Prince made you do it.

00:16:54.480 --> 00:16:58.313
But don't forget,
for every task Javvy brings you,

00:16:58.938 --> 00:17:01.813
you have the right to decide
whether to accept it or not.

00:17:03.563 --> 00:17:05.605
You can save those innocent people.

00:17:06.688 --> 00:17:07.980
It's all up to you.

00:17:12.688 --> 00:17:14.021
You hopeless brat.

00:17:17.146 --> 00:17:19.355
Be quick and make up your mind.

00:18:08.355 --> 00:18:12.146
I retrieved surveillance footage
from the area where the girl went missing.

00:18:12.230 --> 00:18:14.271
There's no sign of Chen Chi-sha.

00:18:14.355 --> 00:18:17.230
But we can infer from
these three crime scenes

00:18:17.313 --> 00:18:20.771
that Chen Chi-sha's whereabouts
should be within this triangle.

00:18:20.855 --> 00:18:23.480
WANG YU-CHING,
HEILUNG HQ, SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

00:18:24.355 --> 00:18:27.230
There were other victims. At least six.

00:18:27.313 --> 00:18:30.355
Fu said there were other souls
that couldn't be summoned.

00:18:30.438 --> 00:18:34.688
It could be the work of Chen Chi-sha too.
I'll find out if they were in this area.

00:18:44.021 --> 00:18:46.188
-What?
-You saw Liu Kuan-fu again.

00:18:46.980 --> 00:18:48.146
Didn't it make you mad?

00:18:53.688 --> 00:18:54.521
Of course.

00:18:55.730 --> 00:18:57.355
But catching bad guys is your job.

00:18:57.855 --> 00:19:00.230
What if the law can't touch him?

00:19:02.021 --> 00:19:04.521
He might escape the law,
but he can't escape karma.

00:19:05.313 --> 00:19:09.188
With so many wronged spirits
out for revenge, I'd have to get in line.

00:19:12.271 --> 00:19:13.188
Let's go.

00:19:32.646 --> 00:19:36.896
Hey, go and get the tea Chan sent me.

00:19:36.980 --> 00:19:38.730
-I'll compare the two.
-Yes, boss.

00:19:57.313 --> 00:19:58.730
This is so good.

00:20:54.105 --> 00:20:55.480
TAIPEI CITY POLICE DEPARTMENT

00:20:55.563 --> 00:20:56.396
Officer Chao!

00:20:57.688 --> 00:20:59.855
I want to turn myself in. Officer Chao!

00:20:59.938 --> 00:21:00.896
-Yes?
-Officer Chao!

00:21:00.980 --> 00:21:03.230
I'm turning myself in. Lock me up.

00:21:03.313 --> 00:21:05.730
-Officer Chao--
-Mr. Shen, talk to me properly.

00:21:05.813 --> 00:21:07.271
Ghosts are haunting me.

00:21:08.605 --> 00:21:09.771
I'm sorry.

00:21:09.855 --> 00:21:11.438
I'm sorry.

00:21:12.063 --> 00:21:15.146
I'm sorry…

00:21:15.646 --> 00:21:17.938
Officer Chao, save me.

00:21:19.646 --> 00:21:21.605
Those ghosts drove him crazy.

00:21:22.521 --> 00:21:25.813
Officer Chao, I'll confess
to all of Liu Kuan-fu's crimes.

00:21:25.896 --> 00:21:29.563
-I'll turn state witness.
-You'll lose your license if you do.

00:21:29.646 --> 00:21:31.855
It's no use to me if I'm dead.

00:21:31.938 --> 00:21:34.271
I mean it. Save me.

00:21:34.355 --> 00:21:35.396
Save me.

00:21:39.646 --> 00:21:41.396
Where is Chen Chi-sha?

00:21:43.855 --> 00:21:44.688
I know where.

00:21:45.313 --> 00:21:47.896
I'll tell you. I'll tell you everything.

00:21:51.688 --> 00:21:53.771
Shit, you were actually right.

00:21:53.855 --> 00:21:57.105
Those ghosts drove Mr. Shen crazy.
He even told us where Chen is.

00:21:57.188 --> 00:21:58.813
I'll send you the location.

00:22:25.396 --> 00:22:29.146
It's been a while, my old friend.

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:39.188
Didn't you promise to retire?

00:22:39.271 --> 00:22:42.855
Must have taken a lot of lives
to refine so many hellspawn.

00:22:43.355 --> 00:22:44.896
That girl isn't here.

00:22:45.980 --> 00:22:48.438
Wang Yu-ching has other uses.

00:22:51.980 --> 00:22:53.938
So she's with your new apprentice?

00:22:56.188 --> 00:22:57.813
He's not my apprentice.

00:22:59.230 --> 00:23:01.855
Suppose not.
He's more powerful than you.

00:23:01.938 --> 00:23:04.188
His magic is scentless.
Almost fooled even me.

00:23:05.355 --> 00:23:07.896
Two female ghosts work for him.
One calls you uncle?

00:23:09.521 --> 00:23:12.771
She said the Demon King threatened you.
What's that all about?

00:23:19.396 --> 00:23:20.688
Save me.

00:23:21.188 --> 00:23:22.230
Save me.

00:23:24.063 --> 00:23:25.730
-Dad.
-Uncle.

00:23:25.813 --> 00:23:27.313
-Save me.
-Save me.

00:23:27.396 --> 00:23:29.355
-Those two female ghosts.
-Save me.

00:23:29.438 --> 00:23:33.063
The one in white is my niece.
The one in red is my daughter.

00:23:33.646 --> 00:23:36.313
Wu Tien-chi dug up their corpses.

00:23:36.396 --> 00:23:37.855
With the Demon King's power,

00:23:37.938 --> 00:23:41.271
he controlled their souls
and turned them into hellspawn.

00:23:41.355 --> 00:23:43.646
Long time no see, Master Chen.

00:23:47.521 --> 00:23:48.855
Why the cold reception?

00:23:48.938 --> 00:23:52.271
They're threatening me
and monitoring my every move.

00:23:52.355 --> 00:23:53.855
If I don't cooperate,

00:23:53.938 --> 00:23:58.146
Wu Tien-chi will let the souls
of those two girls dissipate.

00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:00.105
Wu Tien-chi?

00:24:01.230 --> 00:24:03.646
DEMON KING ENTICES MAN

00:24:06.313 --> 00:24:07.563
Five years ago,

00:24:07.646 --> 00:24:10.480
you promised to tell me
if the Demon King came back.

00:24:10.563 --> 00:24:12.230
And what if I had told you?

00:24:12.938 --> 00:24:16.396
If you hadn't sealed away
all my magical weapons back then,

00:24:16.480 --> 00:24:19.105
I wouldn't be in this state.

00:24:25.480 --> 00:24:28.188
If you defeat
the Third Crown Prince's agent from above,

00:24:28.688 --> 00:24:31.521
I will free
your precious daughter and niece.

00:24:38.438 --> 00:24:39.271
Dad.

00:24:40.521 --> 00:24:41.855
Save me.

00:24:43.188 --> 00:24:44.438
Dad, save me.

00:25:11.813 --> 00:25:13.438
Karma's caught up with me now.

00:25:15.646 --> 00:25:18.980
It's my fault
that the Demon King came back

00:25:19.063 --> 00:25:20.813
-to hurt you--
-I don't care.

00:25:22.355 --> 00:25:24.021
I'm beyond forgiveness.

00:25:26.813 --> 00:25:29.688
But those two girls are innocent.

00:25:33.563 --> 00:25:35.313
I'm not here to fight you.

00:25:40.313 --> 00:25:44.105
They turned me into a living corpse
so that I can defeat you.

00:27:10.021 --> 00:27:11.271
Where's Wang Yu-ching?

00:27:20.188 --> 00:27:24.021
-I don't want to kill you.
-You're saying that to a dead man?

00:27:24.646 --> 00:27:26.230
See you in hell.

00:28:57.813 --> 00:29:00.105
Nine Dragons Divine Fire Barrier?

00:30:14.688 --> 00:30:16.896
I knew this day would come.

00:30:21.480 --> 00:30:24.688
Full moon, magic array, center.

00:30:56.146 --> 00:30:59.105
That must have been tough, Master Chen.

00:31:07.063 --> 00:31:09.188
DONGFENG MARKET